## ğŸ“– About the game

"Investigate the House" is a text adventure game developed in C# from a Redmi 9A phone. You are a rookie investigator who must explore a mysterious house and uncover its secrets... including a mysterious antagonist named **Neomar**.

Every decision you make will affect the story's development and can lead you to different endings. Can you discover the truth?

## ğŸ® Features

- âœ… **Multiple paths** - Your decisions change the story
- âœ… **Inventory system** - You can collect items (bat, mysterious note)
- âœ… **Different endings** - More than 5 different endings
- âœ… **Original story** - Completely created by Neomar Olivo
- âœ… **Unique characters** - Includes an antagonist with your name
- âœ… **Surprises** - Unexpected events await you

## ğŸš€ How to play

1. At the start, choose "Play" in the main menu
2. Make decisions by typing the option number (1, 2 or 3)
3. Explore different paths to discover all endings
4. Try to survive and complete the mission!

